---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Invisalign Clear Aligners" 
  category="Orthodontics"
  description="Invisalign can straighten your teeth without the hassle of metal braces and wires. Custom removable aligners that are comfortable and virtually invisible."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606811971618-4a6c2c8f7c92?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Straighten Your Teeth Discreetly</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Invisalign can straighten your teeth without the hassle of metal braces and wires. 
        Removable aligners are custom made for each patient, creating a product that is 
        comfortable and virtually invisible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Why Choose Invisalign?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Traditional Braces -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>Traditional Braces</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
          </svg>
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Highly visible metal brackets and wires</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Difficult to clean around brackets</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Food restrictions to avoid damage</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Frequent adjustments and tightening</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Potential for mouth sores and discomfort</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Emergency visits for broken brackets</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Invisalign -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-primary-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>Invisalign</span>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-300 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Nearly invisible clear aligners</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-300 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Removable for easy cleaning</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-300 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Eat whatever you want</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-300 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>No painful tightening appointments</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-300 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Smooth, comfortable plastic</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-300 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>No emergency visits for repairs</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      How Invisalign Works
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Initial Consultation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              We examine your teeth and discuss your goals. Digital scans create a 3D model of your mouth, 
              allowing us to show you exactly how your teeth will move and what your final smile will look like.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>What to expect:</strong> Comprehensive exam, digital photos, iTero 3D scanning
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Custom Treatment Plan</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Using advanced software, we map out the precise movements of your teeth throughout treatment. 
              You'll see a virtual representation of your smile transformation before you even start.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Timeline:</strong> Most treatments take 12-18 months with 20-30 sets of aligners
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Receive Your Aligners</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Your custom aligners are manufactured and delivered to our office. We'll show you how to wear 
              and care for them, and provide you with several sets to take home.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Wear time:</strong> 20-22 hours per day, changing to new aligners every 1-2 weeks
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Monitor Progress</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Regular check-ups ensure your treatment is progressing as planned. We'll make any necessary 
              adjustments and provide you with new aligners as you move through your treatment.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Appointments:</strong> Every 6-8 weeks for monitoring and new aligners
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Conditions Invisalign Can Treat
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Crowding</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          When there isn't enough space for teeth to fit properly
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16V4m0 0L3 8m4-4l4 4m6 0v12m0 0l4-4m-4 4l-4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Spacing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Gaps between teeth that need to be closed
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Overbite</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Upper teeth overlap lower teeth too much
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Underbite</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Lower teeth extend past upper teeth
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Crossbite</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Some upper teeth sit inside lower teeth
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Open Bite</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Upper and lower teeth don't touch when biting down
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Living with Invisalign
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Daily Care & Maintenance</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Wear aligners 20-22 hours per day</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Remove only for eating, drinking, and cleaning</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Clean aligners with lukewarm water and gentle brush</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Store in protective case when not wearing</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Switch to new aligners as directed</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Lifestyle Benefits</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Professional Life</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Speak confidently in meetings and presentations without visible braces
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Social Activities</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Smile naturally in photos and social situations
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Eating & Drinking</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Enjoy all your favorite foods without restrictions
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Oral Hygiene</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Maintain excellent oral health with normal brushing and flossing
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Invisalign vs. Other Options
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
      <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md">
        <thead class="bg-primary-100">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-primary-900">Feature</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-primary-900">Invisalign</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Traditional Braces</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">Clear Braces</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Appearance</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">Nearly Invisible</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">Very Visible</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">Less Noticeable</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Removability</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">Yes</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">No</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">No</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Food Restrictions</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">None</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">Many</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">Many</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Oral Hygiene</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">Easy</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">Difficult</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">Difficult</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Comfort</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">High</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">Moderate</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">Moderate</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Treatment Time</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">12-18 months</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">18-24 months</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">18-24 months</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Ready for Your Invisalign Journey?
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Transform your smile discreetly and comfortably with Invisalign. Schedule a consultation 
        to see if you're a good candidate and learn more about the treatment process.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Invisalign Consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/cosmetic-dentistry" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Cosmetic Dentistry</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Complete smile makeovers</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/teeth-whitening" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Teeth Whitening</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Perfect complement to straight teeth</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/veneers" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Porcelain Veneers</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Alternative for minor alignment issues</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Am I a good candidate for Invisalign?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Invisalign can treat most common orthodontic issues including crowding, spacing, overbites, 
        underbites, and crossbites. The best way to determine candidacy is through a consultation 
        where we'll examine your teeth and discuss your goals.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How much does Invisalign cost?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Invisalign treatment typically costs between $3,500-$8,000, similar to traditional braces. 
        The exact cost depends on your specific case complexity and treatment duration. Many insurance 
        plans cover Invisalign similar to braces, and we offer flexible payment plans.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Will Invisalign affect my speech?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most patients experience little to no speech changes with Invisalign. There may be a slight 
        lisp for the first few days as you adjust, but this typically resolves quickly as you become 
        accustomed to the aligners.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">What happens if I lose or break an aligner?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Contact us immediately if you lose or break an aligner. Depending on your treatment stage, 
        we may recommend moving to the next set early, returning to the previous set, or ordering 
        a replacement. We keep your treatment plan on file to quickly resolve any issues.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>